Author: 0rangevanillac0ke0
Text: “If you have to ask...”  But do you have lots of negative/obsessive thoughts about food or body image or how much you eat? Does new or uncertain food situations make you uncomfortable? Does any of this interfere with your day to day life or things you want to do (I.e going out with friends, trying a new restaurant)?   There’s Abnormal and  “disordered eating” habits and there’s EDs, the line between which gets blurry frequently. If you don’t know, what makes you uncertain that the answer is no?
